\mt2 O
\mt1 Mak
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Mak Osirizir Akar Aghuim…®n ak…®nafarim, an akar faragha itim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar God…®n Otarim Krais Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim…®n m…®ngarim.‚Äù Ak…®nafarir kam e an gari, Iesus a gumazir ingangarir av…®ribar amuamin gavgavim ko ziam itim. Ez…® dughiar a gumazamizibar sure gamiziba, ko dughiar a duar kuraba batogheziba, ko dughiar a gumazamizibar arazir kuraba g…®n amadaziba, e ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven eghaghanir kabar gara kamagh…®n fo, a gavgavir ekiam ko ziar ekiam iti. Iesus a kamagh…®n uab…® d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizibar Otarim.‚Äù Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA gumazamizir av…®riba bagh ovegh ua me givezegh me iniasa ize.‚Äù (N…® Mak 10:45…®n gan.)
\ip Mak Iesus…®n ingangarir av…®ribagh eghani. Egha a Iesus gumazamizibar sure gamizir akar av…®ribagh eghanizir puvat…®. Mak faragha Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim Jon…®n ingangarim, ko Iesus…®n rurim, ko Satan Iesus gifarasa a gakaghorir eghaghanim…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® g…®n e Iesus…®n garima, a gumazir os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateribar apangkufi, egha men sure gami. Ez…® faragha suren gumaziba Iesus amir bizibar m…®ngaribagh fozir puvat…®. Egha me n…®m…®ra n…®m…®ra g…®n dagh fofosi.
\ip E uaghan Iesus…®n apanibar gari, me os…®mt…®zir av…®riba a gar…®si. Ez…® Mak Osirizir Akar Aghuim…®n akar abuananaba, a Iesus aremegha ua d…®kavizir eghaghanim geghari.
\c 1
\ms1 Iesus, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n gun // gumazamizibav k…®masa ize
\mr (Sapta 1:1--3:6)
\s1 Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim, // faragha izava Iesus…®n akam akuri
\r (Matyu 3:1-12; Luk 3:1-9; 3:15-17; Jon 1:19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Kar God…®n Otarim Krais Iesus…®n Akar Aghuim.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Aisaia 40:3; Malakai 3:1; Matyu 11:10; Luk 7:27\x*God fom…®ra uan akam isa, an akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia gan…®ngi. Ez…® an an osiriz…®ma, an ak…®nafarim…®n iti. Akar kamra kara:
\b
\q1 ‚ÄúIa oragh! K…® uan abuir gumazim amadaght…®ma,
\q2 a faragh mang…® n…® bagh tuavim ak…®ram.
\q1 
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Aisaia 40:3; Matyu 3:3; Luk 3:4; Jon 1:15; 1:23\x*Gumazir tiarir mam gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n d…®a ghaze,
\q2 ‚ÄòIa Ekiam bagh tuaviba azen…®va, dar k…®r.‚Äô ‚Äù
\b
\m 
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt Aposel 13:24; 19:4\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim Jon izava gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikiava gumazamiziba rua kamagh…®n akam akuri, ‚ÄúIa navibagh iraght…®, k…® ia rueght…®, God ian arazir kuraba g…®n amadagham.‚Äù
\v 5 An akar kabav geima Judian Distrigh…®n itir nguibaba koma Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir gumazamiziba, me bar iza uan arazir kurabar gun m…®geima, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n me rue.
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ofa Gami 11:22; 2 Atriviba 1:8; Matyu 11:8\x*Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim, an as…®zim kamel…®n ar…®zibar ingarizir iniba ikegha as…®zir inim uan ivariam gike. A inir kaba ikeghava odeziba ko ruarim…®n haniba api.\f + \fr 1:6 \ft N…® kamel ko hanibar m…®ngaribagh foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Aposel 13:25\x*Ez…® an akam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan g…®n izamin gumazim an gavgavim guizbang…®ra nan gavgavim gafira. K…® an m…®n garir puvat…®. K…® uaghan aviragh…®va an dagarir asuabar beniba f…®ran gavgaviba puvat…®.
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Aisaia 44:3; Joel 2:28; Aposel 2:4; 10:45; 1 Korin 12:13\x*K…® d…®pam…®n ia rue, eght…® a g…®n God…®n Duam…®n ia ruam.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus ruez…®ma g…®n Satan a gifarasa // a gakaghori
\r (Matyu 3:13-17; 4:1-11; Luk 3:21-22; 4:1-13)
\p 
\v 9 Dughiar kam Iesus Galilin Distrigh…®n itir nguibam, Nasaret, ategha Jon bagha izez…®ma, a Jordan…®n Fanem…®n a rue.
\v 10 Iesus d…®pam…®n aven ikegha azenan otivav…®ra ikia garima overiam kuiaghir…®z…® God…®n Duam bunbam…®n m…®n m…®ghegha a bagha izaghiri.
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Jenesis 22:2; Onger Akaba 2:7; Aisaia 42:1; Matyu 3:17; 12:18; Mak 9:7; Luk 3:22\x*Ez…® tiarir mam God…®n Nguibam…®n ikiava kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúN…® nan Otarim. K…® guizbang…®ra n…® gifuegha n…® bagha bar akonge.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® God…®n Duam anemadaz…®ma a gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghu.
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Onger Akaba 91:11-13\x*A ghugha, 40plan dughiabar danganir kam…®n itima, Satan a gifarasa a gakaghori. A ruarim…®n itir as…®ziba ko ikia dar torim…®n itima, God…®n enselba an garava an akurvasi.
\s1 Iesus faragha zuir suren gumazibar dei
\r (Matyu 4:12-17; Luk 4:14-15; Matyu 4:18-22; Luk 5:1-11)
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt Mak 6:17\x*Ez…® me Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim, inigha kalabus gat…®z…®ma, Iesus g…®n Galilin Distrigh…®n ghugha God…®n Akar Aghuim akuri.
\v 15 \x - \xo 1:15 \xt Daniel 9:25; Matyu 3:2; Galesia 4:4; Efesus 1:10\x*A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiam otogha g…®fa. God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam rogh…®ra ize. Ia navibagh iragh n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n Akar Aghuim…®n ik…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Dughiar mam Iesus Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n dadarim…®n ghua Saimon uan dozim Andru ko aning…®n garima, aning osiriba baghava uan iver ekiaba akuri. Aning osiriba isa dag…®aba bagha da amadir gumazimning.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Matyu 13:47; Luk 5:1-11\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nan g…®n iz…®t…® k…® guan akakaght…®ma, gua osiriba isi mogh…®n gumazamiziba iniam.‚Äù
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt Matyu 4:20; 19:27; Luk 5:11\x*Ez…® aning an akam baraghav…®ra uan iveba ategha an g…®n zui.
\v 19 Ez…® a mong s…®vagha ghua, Sebedin otarim Jems uan dozim Jon ko aning…®n garima aning uan bot…®n ikiava uan iver ekiabar k…®ri.
\v 20 An aning…®n garav…®ra aning…®n diaz…®ma, aning magh…®ra uan afeziam Sebedi koma an ingangarir gumaziba ataghiz…® me uan bot…®n itima aning Iesus…®n g…®n zui.
\s1 Iesus duar kurar mam batoghez…® // a gumazim ategha azenan ize
\r (Luk 4:31-37)
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Matyu 4:13\x*Ez…® Iesus ko an g…®n zuir darazi Kaperneam…®n ghue. Me zuez…® Sabat otoz…®ma, a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghugha, d…®penir kam…®n aven itir gumazamizibar sure gami.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Matyu 7:28-29\x*A men sure gamima gumazamiziba bar an akam baregha d…®gavir kuram gami. An m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba mati gavgavim itir gumazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®aba. An m…®g…®r…®g…®aba Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazibar m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®n zuir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba d…®gavir kuram gami.\f + \fr 1:22 \ft N…® Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazibar m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\v 23 A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®av…®ra itima gumazir duar kuram apazazir mam God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven izegha dei.
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt Mak 5:7\x*A d…®a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n e damuasa, Nasaret…®n gumazim Iesus? N…® e gas…®ghas…®ghasa ize? K…® n…® g…®fo, n…® God amadazir gumazim, n…® God…®n damazim…®n zuezir gumazim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® n…®m…®ra ik…®, egh gumazir kam ategh azenan izegh.‚Äù
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Mak 9:26\x*Ez…® duar kurar kam Iesus baregha gumazir kam gunabagha arav…®ram azenan ize.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar bizir kam…®n ganigha guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gamigha uarira uarir azangs…®si, ‚ÄúKar manmagh…®n amizir bizim? A suren arazir igiam e gami. A gavgavim itir akabav gei. A uaghan akar gavgavim…®n duar kurabav geima da an akam barasi.‚Äù
\v 28 \x - \xo 1:28 \xt Matyu 4:24\x*An amizir bizibar eghaghanim zuam…®ra Galilin Distrik bar a garui.
\s1 Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribar akuragha me gamiz…® me ghuamaghe
\r (Matyu 8:14-17; Luk 4:38-41)
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus gumazir maba ko God ko m…®geir d…®penim ategha Saimon ko Andrun d…®penim…®n zuima, Jems ko Jon me ko zui.
\v 30 Me ghua garima Saimon…®n asamim ar…®a m…®karzim f…®ava dakozim gir…®ghav itima gumazir maba an gun Iesus m…®gei.
\v 31 Me a m…®kemez…®ma, an a bagha ghuava an dafarim…®n suiragha a ghufe. Ez…® an ar…®mariam anetaghiz…®ma a d…®kavigha dagheba me gan…®di.
\s1 Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribagh amiz…®, // me ua dera
\r (Matyu 8:16-17; Luk 4:40-41)
\p 
\v 32 Guarat…®zir kamra, am…®nim p…®riz…®ma me gumazamizir ar…®mariar kuraba koma gumazamizir av…®rir duar kuraba apazaziba bar me inigha Iesus bagha izi.
\v 33 Nguibar kam…®n itir gumazamiziba bar izava d…®penir kam…®n tiar akam…®n uari akufa.
\v 34 \x - \xo 1:34 \xt Mak 3:11-12; Luk 4:41\x*Ez…® Iesus ar…®mariar guar av…®riba itir gumazamizir av…®riba men ar…®mariabagh amiz…®, me ghuamaghe. A duar kurar av…®riba saram otoghez…®ma da gumazamiziba ategha azenan ize. Duar kuraba a g…®fo, a God…®n Otarim. Ez…® kamagh…®n a ghaze, ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…® suam, K…® God…®n Otarim. Egha a men anogoroke.
\s1 Iesus gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n God ko m…®gei
\r (Luk 4:42-44)
\p 
\v 35 \x - \xo 1:35 \xt Matyu 14:23; Mak 6:46; Luk 4:42\x*Egha am…®mzaraghan am…®nim t…®ghar itima, Iesus d…®kavigha d…®penim ategha ghuava gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ghugha God ko m…®gei.
\v 36 A ghuz…® Saimon uan roroaba ko a buriagharui.
\v 37 Me ghua an apigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamiziba bar n…® buri.‚Äù
\p 
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE nguibar igharazir rogh…®ra kagh itibar mangam. K…® munagh uaghan God…®n akam akunam. K…® bizir kam bagha ize.‚Äù
\v 39 \x - \xo 1:39 \xt Matyu 4:23; 9:35\x*A kamagh…®n m…®kemegha, Galilin Distrigh…®n danganiba bar dagh aruava God ko m…®geir d…®penibar aven God…®n akam akurava gumazamizibagh apazazir duar kuraba batosi.
\s1 Iesus lepa itir gumazir mam gamiz…®ma, a ua dera
\r (Matyu 8:1-4; Luk 5:12-16)
\p 
\v 40 Ez…® gumazir lepa itir mam Iesus bagha izava, an guam…®n aviragha tevimning ap…®righa puv…®ra a gaghori, ‚ÄúN…® fuegh…®va na damight…®, k…® God…®n damazim…®n zuegh ua deraka.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:40 \ft Lepan ar…®mariar fom…®ra Baibel…®n dughiam…®n ikezim ighara. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itir lepan ar…®mariam a igharaghav ami. Fom…®ra ikezim pura m…®karzir ghurghurim gumazir namnabar otifi. Egha uaghan bizir igharaziba sara posi.\f*
\v 41 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n oregha, guizbang…®ra bar an apangkufi. Egha uan agharim isa gumazir kam gat…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ifonge. N…®n m…®karzim zuegh, ua deragh.‚Äù
\v 42 Iesus kamagh…®n m…®g…®av…®ra itima, lepan ar…®mariam zuam…®ra gumazir kam ataghiz…® an m…®karzim ua dera.
\p 
\v 43 Ez…® Iesus gumazir kam amaga akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n a m…®gei,
\v 44 \x - \xo 1:44 \xt Ofa Gami 14:1-32; Mak 3:12; 7:36; Luk 5:14\x*‚ÄúN…® oragh, n…® batozir bizir kam n…® an gun m…®k…®man mark…®. N…® mang…® uan m…®karzim is…® ofa gamir gumazim…®n akagh, egh Moses fom…®ra e m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, n…® ua bagh God…®n ofa damu. Eght…® gumazamiziba fogh suam, n…®n ar…®mariam g…®fa.‚Äù
\v 45 Ez…® gumazir kam Iesus a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n damuan aghuagha, bizir kam…®n gun bar me m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, maburan av…®rim Iesus akuvaz…®ma, a nguibar ekiatam…®n aven azenaram aruir puvat…®. A uab…®ra itir danganim…®n itima, gumazamiziba a bagha tintinibar izav…®ra iti.
\c 2
\s1 Iesus gumazir soroghafariba am…®razir mam gamiz…®ma a ua dera
\r (Matyu 9:1-8; Luk 5:17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus uamategha Kaperneam…®n ghu. A ghua d…®penim…®n itima gumazamizir av…®riba a uamategha izezir akam baraki.
\v 2 Me akar kam baregha izez…®ma d…®penim bar iz…®vaz…® an tiar akam sara iz…®fa. Ez…® Iesus God…®n akam me m…®k…®ri.
\v 3 An akam akurima, gumazir maba soroghafariba am…®razir gumazir mam inigha a bagha izi. Gumazir pumuning ko pumuning akuriam…®n a gisaghpugha izi.
\v 4 Me iza garima d…®penim…®n tiar akam bar iz…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Iesus bagh mangan ibura. Egha me gumazir kam inigha d…®penir siriam…®n ghuavanabogha d…®penir siriam…®n torim gamigha beniba akuriam dafegha anemadaz…®ma a Iesus bagha ghuaghiri.\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Judabar d…®peniba boksiabar m…®n gari. Dar inogoriba puvat…®gha, egha p…®n barafi. Ez…® dar m…®riabar azenan adidiaba iti. Dar d…®penir ak…®niba puvat…®. Me pura nguazim gis…®n dar ingari.\f*
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Luk 7:48\x*Ez…® Iesus gumazir kabar n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n ganigha kamagh…®n soroghafariba am…®razir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan borim, k…® n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®geima, Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba apiaghav ikiava uarira uan navir averiabar kamagh…®n m…®gei,
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jop 14:4; Aisaia 43:25; 1 Jon 1:9\x*‚ÄúGumazir kam tizim bagha kamagh…®n m…®gei? A God…®n danganim iniasava ami! Gumazir k…®nitam gumazir igharazitam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghan kogham. God uab…®ra.‚Äù
\v 8 Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zima, Iesus zuam…®ra uan navir averiam…®n men n…®ghn…®zibagh fogha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa manmaghsua uan navir averiabar aven kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si?
\v 9 K…® akar manam m…®k…®mam? Pura gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, k…® n…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amada. Egh uaghan gumazir k…®nitam kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, n…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh mang…®, egh ua deragh.
\v 10 K…® arazir kam damight…®ma, ia ganigh fogham, Gumazamizibar Otarim a nguazir kam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù
\p Egha kamagh…®n gumazir soroghafariba am…®razim m…®gei,
\v 11 ‚ÄúK…® n…® m…®gei, n…® d…®kavigh uan akuriam inigh d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Matyu 9:33\x*Egha a m…®g…®av…®ra itima me gari gumazir kam d…®kavigha uan akuriam inigha azenan ghu.
\p Gumazamiziba bar an ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha God…®n ziam fa kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE faragha bizir katam…®n ganizir puvat…®!‚Äù
\s1 Iesus uab…®n g…®n mangasa Livain dei
\r (Matyu 9:9-13; Luk 5:27-32)
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Iesus ua Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n m…®riam…®n ghuaghiri. A ghuaghirima, gumazamizir av…®riba izava uari akuvaz…®, a men sure gami.
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Jon 1:43\x*A men sure gamua d…®par m…®riam…®n ghua Alfius…®n otarim Livain garima, a gavman dan…®ngamin dag…®aba isir d…®penim…®n aperaghav iti. Iesus an gara, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan g…®n iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Livai a baregha, d…®kavigha an g…®n zui.\f + \fr 2:14 \ft Matyun ziar igharazim kara, Livai.\f*
\p 
\v 15 Egha g…®n Iesus Livain d…®penim…®n ikiava uan suren gumaziba koma api. Ez…® dag…®aba isir gumazir av…®riba ko arazir kurabagh amir gumazir av…®riba, me uaghan me koma api. Gumazir kamagh…®n amir av…®riba, me uaghan Iesus…®n g…®n arui.
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Matyu 11:19; Luk 15:1-2\x*Me apav…®ra itima, Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazir maba, me uaghan Farisiba, me an ganigha, an suren gumazibar azangs…®si, ‚ÄúA manmaghsua dag…®aba isir gumaziba ko arazir kurabagh amir gumaziba koma api?‚Äù\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Farisibar arazir av…®riba iti. Gumazamizir men arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®ziba me kamagh…®n g…®n…®ghn…®si, me God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®. Farisiba kamagh…®n dag…®aba isir gumazibagh n…®ghn…®si, me Rom…®n gavman bagha dag…®aba isi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me uaghan God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n amuava Rom…®n gumaziba ko arazir kurabagh ami.\f*
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Iesus men azangs…®zim baregha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúAr…®mariaba puvat…®zir gumazamiziba, dokta bagha zuir puvat…®. Gumazamizir ar…®mariaba itibara, me dokta bagha zui. K…® God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumazamiziba bagha izezir puvat…®. K…® gumazamizir arazir kurabagh amibar d…®masa ize!‚Äù
\s1 Me God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba atagharazir arazim bagha // Iesus…®n azangs…®si
\r (Matyu 9:14-17; Luk 5:33-39)
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® dughiar mam Jon…®n suren gumaziba ko Farisin suren gumaziba, me God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba atagh…®rasi. Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba dughiar kam…®n apima gumazir maba Iesus bagha izava kamagh…®n an azangs…®si, ‚ÄúKar manmagh…®n amizir arazim, Jon…®n suren gumaziba ko Farisibar suren gumaziba, me dat…®r…®gh…®n God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba atagh…®razima, n…®n suren gumaziba God ko m…®k…®masa dagheba atagh…®razir puvat…®?‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir amuim…®n ikiamim, a ia ko ik…®t…®, ia a bagha izezir gumazibav k…®mt…® me dagheba ategham, o puvat…®? Puvat…®gham. A me ko ik…®t…® me dagheba atagh…®raghan kogham.
\v 20 Me dagheba atagh…®razir dughiam iti. G…®n dughiam iz…®t…®ma gumazir amuim…®n ikiamim, me me dam a inigh mang…®t…®ma, dughiar kabar me dagheba atagh…®ragham.
\p 
\v 21 ‚ÄúGumazitam inir av…®zir igiatam inigha korotiar ghurim…®n porogha a isamizir puvat…®. A kamagh…®n damigh…®va egh a rut…®, inir av…®zir igiam ekonegh korotiar ghurim gekuigh, anebight…®ma an torim guizbang…®ra bar ekevegham.
\v 22 Eght…® gumazitam wain…®n igiam inigh, a is…®va as…®zir inir m…®sevir ghuritam guruighan kogham. A kamagh…®n damight…®, wain…®n d…®pam g…®n buva anang…®va as…®zir inir ghurir kam abight…®, wain…®n d…®pam nguazim giregham. Eght…® wain ko as…®zir inim v…®rara ikuvigham. A kamagh…®n damuan kogham. A wain…®n igiam inigh as…®zir inir m…®sevir igiamra ruigham.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus Sabat…®n Ekiam
\r (Matyu 12:1-8; Luk 6:1-5)
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 2:23 \xt God…®n Araziba 23:25\x*Egha Iesus Sabat…®n dughiar mam…®n, raiz…®n m…®n garir dagher mam wit, an an azenir ekiam…®n torim…®n zui. Ez…® an suren gumaziba a ko ghuava wit…®n ov…®ziba isi.\f + \fr 2:23 \ft N…® wit…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt God…®n Araziba 23:25\x*Me zuima Farisin maba men ganigha kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan. Me manmaghsua arazir kam gamuava Sabat…®n arazim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®?‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 2:25-26 \xt 1 Samuel 21:6\x*Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDevit amizir bizim, me an osiriz…®ma a iti, ez…® ia ti an ganiz, o puvat…®? A uan adarazi ko m…®tiriam men azima a bizir kam gami.
\v 26 \x - \xo 2:26 \xt Ofa Gami 24:9\x*Devit God…®n Purirpenim…®n aven ghua me ofa damuasa at…®zir bret…®n rubuziba inigha uan adarazi ko me da ame. An da apava, uaghan maba isa uan gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®ma, me uaghan da ame. Dughiar kam Abiatar, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim itima, Devit bret…®n kaba ame. Judabar arazir kam iti. Bret…®n kaba ofa gamir gumazibaram ada api, gumazamizir k…®niba puvat…®. Ez…® Devit, a gumazir k…®nim, egha a bret…®n kaba ame.‚Äù
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 2:27 \xt God…®n Araziba 5:14\x*Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod gumazamizibar akurvaghasa Sabat at…®. A Sabat bagha gumazamiziba at…®zir puvat…®.
\v 28 \x - \xo 2:28 \xt Matyu 12:8\x*Ez…® Gumazamizibar Otarim a Sabat…®n dughiam…®n Ekiam.‚Äù\f + \fr 2:28 \ft N…® Gumazamizibar Otarim…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\c 3
\s1 Iesus Sabat…®n dughiam…®n gumazir dafarim ekonezir mam gamiz…®ma // a ua dera
\r (Matyu 12:9-14; Luk 6:6-11)
\p 
\v 1-2 Egha dughiar igharazir mam Iesus God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n ghua garima, dafarim ekonezir gumazir mam, gumazamizir av…®ribar tong…®n d…®penir kam…®n aven iti. A itima gumazir maba uaghan iti. Me, Iesus bizitam damight…®, me akam agasasa bar derav…®ram an gari. Me kamaghsua an gari. A Sabat…®n gumazir kam…®n akuragham, o?
\v 3 Me bizir kam bagha an garav…®ra itima, Iesus kamagh…®n dafarim ekonezir gumazim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh iz…® bar en guam…®n tugh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Luk 14:3\x*Gumazim d…®kavigha tuz…®ma, Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúArazir manam Sabat…®n arazim ab…®ki? E arazir aghuim damuam, o arazir kuram damuam, o gumazim…®n akuragham, o gumazim gas…®ghas…®gham?‚Äù A kamagh…®n men azaraz…®ma, me bar n…®m…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Jon 11:33\x*An damazimning bar gumazamizibagh aruava, navim…®n aven men atari. A men garima, men naviba gavgavigha apangkuvir n…®ghn…®ziba men puvat…®. Kamagh…®n a bar osemegha gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan dafarim onegh.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam uan dafarim onez…®ma, an dafarim ua dera.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Matyu 22:15-16\x*Ez…® Farisiba kamagh…®n ganigha d…®penim ategha azenan ghuegha Herot…®n gumaziba ko ikia Iesus m…®soghasa akabar k…®ri.
\ms1 Iesus uan gavgavim men akaz…®ma an adarazi n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim // an itir puvat…®
\mr (Sapta 3:7--6:6)
\s1 Gumazamizir av…®riba Iesus…®n g…®n zui
\r (Luk 6:17-19)
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n ghuaghiri. A ghuaghirima gumazamizir av…®riba Galilin Distrigh…®n ikegha an g…®n ghuaghiri.
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Matyu 4:25\x*Gumazamizir av…®riba Judian Distrik ko, Jerusalem…®n nguibam ko, Idumean Distrik ko, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n itir danganiba ko, Tair ko Saidon…®n nguibamning…®n ikegha Iesus bagha ghuaghiri. Gumazamizir av…®rir kaba, me an amizir bizibar akam baregha a bagha ghuaghiri.
\v 9-10 \x - \xo 3:9-10 \xt Matyu 9:21; 14:36; Mak 4:1; Mak 5:29; 6:56; Luk 5:1-3; Luk 7:21\x*Me iraghuez…®ma, Iesus gumazamizir av…®ribar akuraz…®ma, men ar…®mariaba g…®fa. Ar…®mariaba itir gumazamizir av…®riba uan ar…®mariaba ag…®vasa Iesus…®n borogh…®n uari akuvagha, Iesus…®n suighasa uari munamadi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Iesus uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bot…®n tam inigh iz…® puram anet…®ght…® a ik…®. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar na akuvaght…®ma k…® bot…®n ghuavanangam.‚Äù
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt Mak 1:23-24; Luk 4:41\x*Iesus me m…®geima, duar kuraba apazazir gumazir maba iza, Iesus…®n gara duar kuraba zuam…®ra me gamima me Iesus…®n guam…®n daighira kamagh…®n d…®a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n Otarim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt Matyu 8:4; 12:16; Mak 1:34\x*Me kamagh…®n m…®geima, a men anogorogha ghaze, me an gun gumazir igharazibav k…®man mark…®.
\s1 Iesus 12plan aposelba me am…®sefe
\r (Matyu 10:1-4; Luk 6:12-16)
\p 
\v 13 Egha Iesus d…®par m…®riam…®n ikegha d…®kavigha m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabogha uan ifongezir gumazibar diaz…®ma, me a bagha zui.
\v 14 Me zuima a gumazir 12pla m…®sevegha ziar kam, aposelba, me gat…®. Eght…® me a ko ik…®t…®, a g…®n me amang…®t…® me mang…® God…®n Akar Aghuim akunam.
\v 15 Egh a uan gavgavim me dan…®ngt…®ma me uaghan duar kuraba batogham.
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Jon 1:42\x*A m…®sevezir gumazir 12plan ziabar kara. Saimon (Iesus g…®n ziar kam, Pita, a gat…®),
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Luk 9:54\x*Sebedin otarimning Jems ko Jon (A ziar kam aning gat…®, Boanerges. Ziar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, atara pamtem m…®geir gumazimning),
\v 18 Andru ko Filip, Bartolomyu, Matyu, Tomas, Alfius…®n otarim Jems, Tadius, Saimon (a Selotbar gumazir mam),
\v 19 ko Judas Iskariot, gumazir Iesus isava, apanibagh an…®ngizim.
\s1 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, // ‚ÄúIesus Belsebul…®n gavgavim…®n ingari.‚Äù
\r (Matyu 12:24-32; Luk 11:14-23; 12:10)
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Mak 6:31\x*Egha Iesus uamategha d…®penim…®n aven ghugha itima gumazamizir av…®riba izava anekufa. Me bar anekufa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uan suren gumaziba ko daghebar aman ibura. Me damamin dughiaba puvat…®.
\v 21 \x - \xo 3:21 \xt Jon 7:5; 10:20\x*Ez…® gumazamizir maba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAn ongani.‚Äù Ez…® Iesus…®n adarazi akar kam baregha, a inigh mangasa izi.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 3:22 \xt Matyu 9:34; 10:25\x*Ez…® Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazir maba Jerusalem…®n ikegha izaghira kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBelsebul a gapasa. A duar kurabar gumazir dapanim…®n gavgavim…®n duar kuraba batosi.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:22 \ft Satan…®n ziar mamra kara, Belsebul.\f*
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 3:23 \xt Matyu 4:10; Luk 11:17-22\x*Ez…® Iesus me m…®geir akam baregha, egha kamagh…®n gumazamizibar diagha akar is…®n zuir mabar me m…®gei, ‚ÄúSatan manmagh…®n uab…®ra uab…® batuegham?
\v 24 Kantrin tam…®n gumazamiziba uari tuiragh uarira uariv soght…®, kantrin kam ikian kogham.
\v 25 Eght…® d…®penir vam…®ran itir darazi uari abigh uarira uariv sogh d…®penir kam…®n itir darazi ikian kogham.
\v 26 Kamagh…®ra Satan uan adarazi ko uari abigh uariv sogh, egh me manmagh…®n tugh gavgavigh bizibar ganamin gavgavim ikiam? Bar puvat…®gham.
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 3:27 \xt Aisaia 49:24; Matyu 12:29\x*‚ÄúEght…® gumazir manatam puram aven mang…® gumazir gavgavitam…®n d…®penim akarigh…®va an biziba okemegham? Puvat…®gham. A faragh…®v…®ra benibar gumazir gavgavir kam ikegham. A kamagh…®n a damigh, egh gumazir kam…®n d…®penim…®n aven mang…®, an biziba okemegham.
\p 
\v 28 \x - \xo 3:28-29 \xt Matyu 12:31-32; Luk 12:10; 1 Jon 5:16\x*‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ko me God…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®zir akaba, God da g…®n amangamin tuavim iti.
\v 29 Eght…® gumazitam God…®n Duam…®n ziam gas…®ghasight…®ma God an arazir kurar kam, a g…®n amadaghan kogham. Egh gumazir kam aremeght…®, arazir kurar kam an ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Me faragha kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúDuar kurar mam a gapasa.‚Äù A bizir kam bagha, akar kabar me m…®gei.\f + \fr 3:30 \ft Iesus God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim…®n ingari. Ez…® me ghaze, a Satan…®n gavgavim…®n ingari. Me kamagh…®n God…®n Duam…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®si.\f*
\s1 Iesus…®n amebam ko an doziba
\r (Matyu 12:46-50; Luk 8:19-21)
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 3:31 \xt Mak 6:3; Jon 2:12; Aposel 1:14\x*Ez…® Iesus…®n amebam ko doziba izava, a itir d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n tughava gumazir mam amadaz…®ma a Iesus m…®k…®masa aven zui.
\v 32 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba a koma apiaghav ikia kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, n…®n amebam ko doziba n…® bagha izeghava azenan iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 33 Me a m…®kemez…®ma a kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúTina nan amebam? Te nan doziba?‚Äù
\p 
\v 34 A kamagh…®n men azaragha, egha an okarigha apiaghav itir gumazamizibar gara, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gan! Nan amebam ko dozibara kara.
\v 35 Gumazamizir God ifongezir arazibar g…®n zuiba, me nan doziba ko nan amiziba ko nan amebam.‚Äù
\c 4
\s1 Iesus akar is…®n zuim…®n kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir mam wit…®n ov…®ziba inigha azenim…®n da akuragharui.‚Äù
\r (Matyu 13:1-23; Luk 8:4-15)
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt Mak 3:7-9; Luk 5:1-3\x*Dughiar igharazir mam Iesus ua d…®par m…®riam…®n ikiava, gumazamizir mabar sure gami. Me an akaba baraghasa anekuvagha guizbang…®ra bar av…®raseme. Ez…® a bot…®n mam…®n b…®ragha d…®pam gis…®n aperaghav iti. Gumazamizir kaba an borogh…®n dadarim…®n apiaghav iti.
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt Matyu 13:34; Mak 4:33-34\x*An akar is…®n zuir av…®ribar men sure gamuava, kamagh…®n me m…®gei,
\v 3 ‚ÄúIa oragh. Gumazir mam raiz…®n m…®n garir daghem wit, ana da inigha ghua azenim…®n da akuragharui.
\v 4 An ada akurima wit…®n ov…®zir maba tuavim…®n irez…®ma, kuaraziba iza da ame.
\v 5 Ez…® maba dag…®abagh is…®n itir nguazir evarim gire. Nguazir kam m…®temezir puvat…®, ez…® wit…®n ov…®ziba zuam…®ra afuangi.
\v 6 Ez…® dar biba bar nguazim…®n aven iraghuezir puvat…®z…®, aruem anaga dagh isiraz…®, da isia m…®s…®ngi.
\v 7 Ez…® wit…®n ov…®zir maba benir d…®koniba itir nguazim giregha, benibar tong…®n afuangiz…®, benir d…®koniba aghuava da ikiaghar…®ki. Ez…® dar ov…®ziba m…®sevezir puvat…®.
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt Matyu 13:8; Luk 8:8; Jon 15:5; Kolosi 1:6\x*Ez…® wit…®n ov…®zir maba nguazir aghuim giregha aghuava dagheba m…®sefi. Egha maba 30plan ov…®ziba m…®sevima maba 60plan ov…®ziba m…®sefe. Ez…® maba 100plan ov…®ziba m…®sefe.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus manmaghsuav…®ra // akar is…®n zuibagh ami
\r (Matyu 13:10-17; Luk 8:9-10)
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® gumazamizir av…®riba bar ghuez…®, Iesus uab…®ra itima, an 12plan gumaziba ko an borogh…®n itir gumazamiziba, me an akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim bagha an azara.
\v 11 Me an azaraz…®ma a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod fofozim ia gan…®ngiz…®ma, ia God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n akar mogomebagh fo. Egha k…® azenan itir gumazamiziba pura akar is…®n zuibar me m…®gei.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4:12 \xt Aisaia 6:9-10; Jon 12:40; Aposel 28:26-27\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma:
\b
\q1 ‚Äú ‚ÄòMe zurara gan…®va,
\q2 egh deragh bizitam…®n ganighan kogham.
\q1 Me uaghan zurara oragh…®va,
\q2 egh me deragh bizitam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghan kogham.
\q1 Me amuava akar m…®ngarim g…®fogha,
\q2 uan navibagh iraz…®,
\q3 God men arazir kuraba g…®n amadaghai.‚Äô ‚Äù\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Iesus God…®n g…®n mangasa gumazamizibar anogorozir puvat…®. Marazi uari God…®n g…®n mangan aghua.\f*
\s1 Wit…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim
\r (Matyu 13:18-23; Luk 8:11-15)
\p 
\v 13 An akar kam ua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa wit…®n akar is…®n zuir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foz, o puvat…®? Ia manmagh…®n akar is…®n zuir igharazir tabagh fogham?
\v 14 Akar is…®n zuim…®n aven itir gumazir kam, a mati gumazir God…®n akam akuragharuim.
\v 15 Gumazamizir maba tuavim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baraghiz…®, Satan zuam…®ra iza me oraghizir God…®n akaba, me dama ada ini.
\v 16 Gumazamizir maba dag…®aba itir nguazim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baregha da bagha bar akonge.
\v 17 Egha men biba iraghuezir puvat…®gha, uaghan dughiar ruarim…®n ikezir puvat…®. Me itima os…®mt…®ziba ko God…®n g…®n zuir gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®zir araziba izima, me pura God ataki.
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Matyu 13:26\x*Gumazamizir maba benir d…®koniba itir nguazim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baraki.
\v 19 \x - \xo 4:19 \xt Matyu 19:23-24; 1 Timoti 6:9; 6:17\x*Me da baregha uaghan nguazir kam…®n biziba bagha n…®ghn…®gha, dag…®ar av…®riba iniasa ifavarir n…®ghn…®zibagh amua, nguazir kam…®n bizir av…®ribar garava da bagha agoi. Bizir kabar n…®ghn…®ziba izava God…®n akaba ikiaghar…®ghiz…® da m…®sevir puvat…®.
\v 20 Ez…® gumazamizir maba nguazir aghuim girezir wit…®n ov…®zibar m…®n ami. Me God…®n akaba baregha dar suiragha dar g…®n zui. Gumazamizir kaba mati wit…®n ov…®ziba m…®s…®va, maba 30plan ov…®ziba m…®sevima, maba 60plan ov…®ziba m…®sevima maba 100plan ov…®ziba m…®sefe.‚Äù
\s1 Lam…®n danganimra aneguragh
\r (Luk 8:16-18)
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 4:21 \xt Matyu 5:15; Luk 11:33\x*Egha Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIan tina lam gaborogha a inigha itarir ekiam…®n anevara? O an a inigha dakozim…®n apengan anet…®? Puvat…®! Ia lam daborogh a inigh azenan an danganimram aneguragh.
\v 22 \x - \xo 4:22 \xt Matyu 10:26; Luk 12:2\x*Kamagh…®ra mogomer biziba da g…®n azenan otivigham. Eght…® bizir amigha aveziba da uaghan g…®n azenan otivigham.
\v 23 Tina kuarimning iti, an oragh.‚Äù\f + \fr 4:23 \ft Iesus akar is…®n zuibar gumazamizibar sure gami. A kamagh…®n foghasa, me guizbang…®ra God gifongez ti puvat…®. Gumazir God gifongeziba, akar is…®n zuiba baregha, dagh n…®ghn…®ghava g…®n dar m…®ngaribar gara dagh fo. Ez…® gumazir God gifongezir puvat…®ziba, n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, akar is…®n zuiba, eghaghanir onganiba. Kamagh…®n me akar is…®n zuiba, dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha, dar m…®ngaribar garir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 24-25 \x - \xo 4:24-25 \xt Matyu 7:2; Matyu 13:12; 25:29; Luk 6:38; Luk 19:26\x*Egha a ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deraghv…®ra akar kam baragh. Gumazitam o amizitam God…®n akabagh foght…®, God uan akabar fofozir igharaziba a dan…®ngam, eght…® a God…®n akar av…®ribagh fogham. Eght…® God…®n akabagh foghan aghuazir gumazim o amizim, an fofozir muziarim God a dam a inigham.‚Äù
\s1 Dagher ov…®zir afuarazibar akar is…®n zuim
\p 
\v 26 Egha Iesus m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n arazim a kamak…®n. Gumazir mam dagher ov…®ziba inigha nguazim…®n da akuri.
\v 27 \x - \xo 4:27 \xt Jems 5:7\x*Gumazir kam da kunigha, d…®magaribar akuava, aruebar d…®kavigha arui. An aruima dagher ov…®zir kaba da afuegha aghui. Dagher ov…®zir kaba manmagh…®n afuegha aghui? Gumazir kam fozir puvat…®.
\v 28 Ez…® nguazimra dagher ov…®zir kabagh amiz…®ma da aghua m…®sefe. Da faragha afuegha aghua ghua aghariba otivigha, ada ghua ak…®mariba otivigha m…®sefe.
\v 29 \x - \xo 4:29 \xt Joel 3:13; Akar Mogomem 14:15-18\x*Da m…®sevegha dagheba itima, gumazir kam sabam inigha dar akori. A fo, dagheba iti, ez…® da akoramin dughiam oto.‚Äù
\s1 Mastet…®n ov…®zim…®n akar is…®n zuim
\r (Matyu 13:31-32; Luk 13:18-19)
\p 
\v 30 Egha a ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE manmagh…®n God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n arazim m…®k…®mam? O, e akar is…®n zuir manam…®n an m…®ngarim…®n gun m…®k…®mam?
\v 31 A mastet…®n ov…®zim…®n m…®n gari. Mastet…®n zuravarir ov…®ziba bar sufi. Temer igharazibar ov…®ziba bar a gafiragha ekefe.\f + \fr 4:31 \ft N…® mastet…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\v 32 Gumazir mam anekuniz…®ma a g…®n aghua bar ekevegha azenim…®n itir zuravariba bar dagh afiragha bar ekefe. An ekevegha an aguar ekiaba uari tuiraz…®ma kuaraziba izava an aguabar dughuazim…®n aven ikia m…®konibar ingari.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus akar is…®n zuibara akam akuri
\r (Matyu 13:34-35)
\p 
\v 33 Egha Iesus men n…®ghn…®ziba tuz…®nagh…®ra, an akar is…®n zuir av…®ribar God…®n akabar me m…®gei.
\v 34 An akabar gumazamizibav g…®ava zurara akar is…®n zuibar me m…®gei. Egha a uan suren gumaziba ko me uarira ikiava a bizibar m…®ngariba ab…®gha me m…®gei.
\s1 Iesus am…®nir ekiam ko d…®pavs…®zim batoghez…® aning pura n…®m…®ra ir…®ghav iti
\r (Matyu 8:23-27; Luk 8:22-25)
\p 
\v 35 Aruer kam…®n am…®nim p…®rasava amima Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE d…®par kam abigh an vong…®n mangam.‚Äù
\v 36 A kamagh…®n me m…®geima gumazamiziba dadarim…®n ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® me Iesus aperaghav itir bot…®n ghuavanabogha pul gamua vong…®n zui. Bot…®n igharazir maba uaghan me ko vong…®n zui.
\v 37 Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko zuima, Maia! Am…®nir ekiam d…®kafi. Ez…® d…®pavs…®ziba izava bot gafiraz…® d…®pam bot…®n aven ghuaghira, bot giz…®vaz…®, an atam d…®pam…®n aven mag…®rasava ami.
\p 
\v 38 Bot mag…®rasava amima, Iesus bot…®n kam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n dapanir aghoghonir mam uan dapanim…®n aghorogha akui. Ez…® an suren gumaziba a gaghuragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, e g…®fa! N…® e bagha n…®ghn…®si, o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p 
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus d…®kavigha akar gavgavim am…®nim gan…®ga, egha kamagh…®n ongarim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua am…®ragh, n…®m…®ra ik…®!‚Äù A m…®geima, am…®nim am…®raz…®, d…®pam pura n…®m…®ra ir…®ghav iti.
\p 
\v 40 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha puv atiati? Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim oteveghav…®ra iti?‚Äù
\p 
\v 41 Ez…® me bar atiatigha kamagh…®n uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúKar gumazir manmagh…®n amizim? A m…®geima, am…®nim ko d…®pavs…®zim an akam barasi!‚Äù
\c 5
\s1 Iesus Gerasan gumazir mam…®n duar kuraba batoghez…®ma da anetaki
\r (Matyu 8:28-34; Luk 8:26-39)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko d…®pam abigha vong…®n Gerasan danganim…®n oto.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Mak 1:23\x*Me otivigha, Iesus bot ategha dadarim…®n anadima gumazir duar kuram apazazir mam, a matmatiam…®n tong…®n ikegha Iesus bativasa izi.
\v 3-4 A matmatiam…®n ikiava a gakui. Me dughiar av…®riba senbar an agharimning ikiava, ankavba an suemning gazui. Ez…® a zurara sen…®n kabar suigha da aghora egha an suemning ikezir ankavbav sogha da aghoraghar…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazitam gumazir kam…®n suiragh a ik…®va avegham. Me uaghan senbar a ikeght…® da an suiraghan kogham. Egh gumazitam gavgavigh a ikeghan kogham.
\v 5 A d…®magariba ko aruebar matmatiam ko m…®ghs…®abar purama arua pamtem arava dag…®abar uab…® uan m…®karzim aghori.
\p 
\v 6 A saghon ikia Iesus…®n ganigha ivegha a bagha izava an guam…®n uan tevimning ap…®ri.
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 5:7-8 \xt Mak 1:24\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n duar kuram m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® duar kuram, n…® gumazir kam ategh azenan iz…®.‚Äù
\p Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®geima, gumazir kam pamtem ara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmagh…®n na damuasa, Iesus, God…®n Bar P…®n Itim…®n Otarim. K…® God…®n damazim…®n pamtem n…®n azangs…®si, n…® arazir kuratam na damuam mark…®!‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt Luk 8:30\x*A kamagh…®n m…®geima Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan ziam d…®borogh.‚Äù
\p Ez…® duar kurar kam a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bar av…®raseme, kamagh…®n nan ziam Av…®riba.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 A Iesus danganir igharazitam…®n me amangan aghuagha Iesus v…®v…®gha a gakaghori.
\p 
\v 11 Dughiar kam, men borogh…®ra itir m…®ghs…®ar m…®riam…®n dar av…®riba ikiava api.
\v 12 Ez…® duar kurar kaba kamagh…®n Iesus m…®g…®ava a gakaghori, ‚ÄúN…® e m…®kemegh e amadaght…® e mang…® dar okoruar munam gapazaka.‚Äù
\v 13 Ez…® a men amamangat…®z…® duar kurar kaba gumazir kam ategha azenan izegha ghua dabagh apasa. Dar av…®rir kaba, dar d…®bobonim 2,000…®n borogh…®n ghu. Ez…® daba puv ivemara ghua davarir kuram giraghuegha d…®pam…®n aven ghuegha d…®pam apava ariaghire.
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® dabar garir gumaziba daba batoghezir bizim…®n ganigha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n ghua danganir kam…®n itir nguibar dozibar ghua bizir otozir kam…®n gun m…®gei. Ez…® gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n ganasa d…®kavigha izi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Luk 8:27; 8:35\x*Me iza Iesus…®n borogh…®n duar kuraba apazazir gumazim…®n garima, an n…®ghn…®zim ua deraz…®, a korotiaba aghuigha aperaghav iti. Me an ganigha atiati.
\v 16 Ez…® otozir bizir kam…®n ganizir gumazamiziba, me duar kuraba apazazir gumazim batozir bizir kabar gumazir igharazibav gei. Me dar gun m…®g…®a uaghan daba batozir bizim…®n gun m…®gei.
\v 17 Egha gumazamizir kaba bizir kam baregha iza an gara a gakaghora ghaze, a men nguazim ategh danganir igharazitam…®n mang…®.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Iesus danganir kam ategh mangasa bot…®n b…®rima duar kuraba apazazir gumazim Iesus ko mangasa pamtem a gaghori.
\v 19 Ez…® Iesus an anogoregha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan adarazi bagh d…®penim…®n mang…®va Ekiam n…®n akuragha n…® gamizir bizibar gun me m…®k…®m…®va, a uaghan bar n…®n apangkuvizir bizim…®n gun me m…®k…®m.‚Äù
\v 20 \x - \xo 5:20 \xt Matyu 4:25; Mak 7:31\x*Ez…® gumazir kam a baregha ghua Iesus an akurazir bizim…®n gun Dekapolis…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibabar ghua bar me m…®gei. Gumazamizir kaba a baregha d…®gavir kuram gami.
\s1 Iesus aremezir guivir mam ko, ar…®mariar amizir mam gamiz…® // aning ua dera
\r (Matyu 9:18-26; Luk 8:40-56)
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Iesus bot inigha uamategha d…®pam…®n vong…®n ize. A izegha d…®par dadarim…®n itima, gumazamizir av…®riba izava anekufa.
\v 22-23 \x - \xo 5:22-23 \xt Matyu 8:3; Mak 7:32\x*Ez…® God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n bizibar garir gumazir mam, an ziam Jairus, a iza Iesus…®n gara an guam…®n uab…® ekunigha an dagarimning…®n borogh…®n ir…®gha kamagh…®n puv…®ram a gaghori, ‚ÄúNan guivim aremeghasa an d…®ghorimra isi. N…® iz…®va uan dafarim a dat…®ght…® an ar…®mariam g…®vagh ua ikiam.‚Äù
\v 24 Ez…® Iesus a ko zui.
\p A zuima gumazamizir av…®rim bar anekuvagha an g…®n zui.
\v 25 Me zuima men tong…®n amizir 12plan azenibar ghuzim batir ar…®mariam itir mam uaghan me ko zui. Amizir kam ghuzim batir ar…®mariam an itima 12plan azeniba g…®fa.
\v 26 A fom…®ra ar…®mariam ag…®vasa doktaba bagha zuima, me an ar…®mariam a g…®vazir puvat…®. Ez…® a m…®zazir kuram isi. A uan ar…®mariam ag…®vasa pura uan dag…®abar me givezima an dag…®aba bar g…®fa. Bizir kaba an ar…®mariam…®n akurazir puvat…®. An ek…®va ghuav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 27-28 \x - \xo 5:27-28 \xt Matyu 14:36\x*A Iesus amir bizibar akam baregha, kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúK…® puram an azenan itir korotiamra suiragh nan ar…®mariam g…®vagham.‚Äù A kamagh…®n n…®ghnigha egha damuasa. Amizir kam gumazamizir av…®ribar g…®n izava me munamaga iza Iesus…®n korotiar av…®zim…®n suira.
\v 29 Amizim Iesus…®n korotiam…®n suizir dughiamra, an ghuzir ar…®mariam pura dutugha ghu. A uab…® baregha fo, an m…®karzim ua dera.
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 5:30 \xt Luk 5:17; 6:19; 8:46\x*A kamagh…®n amimra, Iesus zuam…®ra uab…® baregha God gumazamizibar ar…®mariaba g…®vaghasa a gan…®ngizir gavgavim, an m…®karzim ataghiz…® a fo, nan gavgavim ingari. Egha a ragha gumazamizibar garava men azara, ‚ÄúTina nan korotiam…®n suira?‚Äù
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® an suren gumaziba a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® garima, gumazamizir av…®riba n…® akufa. Ez…® n…® tizim bagha kamagh…®n azai, ‚ÄòTina nan korotiam…®n suira?‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Me kamagh…®n Iesus m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Iesus an korotiam…®n suirazir gumazim o amizim g…®foghasa ragh…®r…®gha garagharui.
\v 33 A ruiav…®ra itima, amizir kam a batozir bizim g…®fogha iza Iesus…®n guam…®n degiaghir…®gha, atiatia n…®gha guizbang…®ra a batozir bizim…®n gun m…®gei.
\v 34 \x - \xo 5:34 \xt Mak 10:52; Luk 7:50; 17:19; Aposel 14:9\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan guivim, n…® navim bar am…®ragh ik…®. N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan iti. Kamagh…®n, n…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…® gamiz…® n…® dera. N…® navir am…®rizim sara mang…®, eght…® n…®n ar…®mariar kam ua n…® damuan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 35 Iesus amizir kam m…®g…®av…®ra itima gumazir maba God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n bizibar garir gumazim, Jairus…®n d…®penim…®n ikegha iza kamagh…®n Jairus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n guivim areme. N…® os…®mt…®zim Tisa dan…®ngan mark…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 36 Me kamagh…®n m…®geima Iesus me baregha kamagh…®n Jairus m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atiatingan mark…®. N…® pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ik…®.‚Äù
