\v 40 \x - \xo 5:40 \xt Matyu 9:25; Luk 8:54; Jon 11:11\x*A kamagh…®n me m…®geima, me a d…®pova an ingarava kava uariv gei, ‚ÄúE fo, a guizbang…®ram areme.‚Äù Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n m…®geima, a bar me batuegha guivim…®n afeziam ko amebam inigha an suren gumazir pumuning ko m…®kezim, merara a ko zui. A me inigha me guivim…®n kuam itir danganim…®n aven ghue.
\v 41 \x - \xo 5:41 \xt Luk 7:14\x*Me ghuegha a guivim…®n dafarim…®n suiragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúTalita kum!‚Äù (Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n iti, ‚ÄúGuivir dozim, k…® n…® m…®gei, n…® d…®kafigh!‚Äù)
\v 42 An a m…®geimrama, guivim d…®kavigha tughava arui. (An azenir 12pla.) A d…®kavigha tugha aruima, me kamagh…®n guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gami.
\v 43 \x - \xo 5:43 \xt Mak 1:44; 7:36; Luk 8:55\x*Ez…® an akar gavgavim…®n guizbang…®ra me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia bizir kam…®n gun gumazir igharazitam m…®k…®mam mark…®. A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava daghetam a dan…®ngasa me m…®gei.
\c 6
\s1 Iesus…®n nguibam…®n itir darazi // an aghuagha ak…®rim a gasara
\r (Matyu 13:53-58; Luk 4:16-30)
\p 
\v 1 Egha Iesus danganir kam ategha uan nguibam…®n ghuavanadima an suren gumaziba a ko zui.
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Jon 7:15\x*Ez…®, Sabat…®n dughiam otoz…® a God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven ghua, gumazamizibar sure gami. Gumazamizir av…®riba an akaba baregha d…®gavir kuram gami.
\p Me d…®gavir kuram gamigha kamagh…®n azai, ‚ÄúGumazir kam managh akar kaba ini? A managh n…®ghn…®zir aghuir kaba ini? A uaghan managh mirakelbagh amir gavgavir kam ini?
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt Jon 6:42\x*E fo, kar pura d…®penibar ingarir gumazim. A Marian otarim, egha a Jems ko Josep, Judas, ko Saimon, a men avebam. An buaramiziba e ko iti.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me d…®bovir akabar a m…®g…®ava navibar aven an atari.
