\v 4 \x - \xo 6:4 \xt Matyu 13:57; Luk 4:24; Jon 4:44\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGod…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, a nguibar igharazibar zuima, me an ziam fe. Ez…® an nguibam…®n an adarasi, me an ziam fer puvat…®.‚Äù
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a nguibar kam…®n mirakel…®n av…®ribagh amizir puvat…®. A pura dafarim ar…®mariar gumazir vabaram ar…®ghiz…®ma, men ar…®mariaba g…®fa.
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt Matyu 9:35; Luk 13:22\x*Ez…® me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®z…®ma, a kamagh…®n d…®gavir kuram gami.
\ms1 Iesus uan gavgavim suren gumazibar akaz…®, me deragha a g…®fozir pu
\mr (Sapta 6:6--8:21)
\s1 Iesus uan 12plan aposelba ingangarim me ganigha me amada
\r (Matyu 10:5-15; Luk 9:1-6)
\p Egha Iesus nguibabagh arua gumazamizibar sure gami.
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt Luk 10:1\x*Iesus men sure gamua, egha 12plan aposelbar diaz…®, me a bagha izez…®, a me akuvagha, me m…®g…®a me amada. Gumazir pumuning uaning inigha zui, ez…® gumazir pumuning uaning inigha zui. A kamagh…®n amua uaghan duar kuraba batoghamin gavgavim me ganigha me amada.
