\v 8-9 \x - \xo 6:8-9 \xt Matyu 10:9-10\x*\x - \xo 6:8-11 \xt Luk 10:4-11\x*A m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam me gamuava me amada, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, bizitaba uari bagh da inian mark…®. Ia bret…®n tam ko m…®taritam inian mark…®. Ia dag…®atam suighan mark…®. Ia uan dagarir asuaba aghuva, ua siot…®n tam inian mark…®. Ia uan aghorir asadivibara suigh mang…®.
\v 10 Ia kamagh…®n damigh, d…®penir ia aven zuir manam, ia d…®penir kamra ik…®, mang…® dughiar ia nguibar kam atagh…®raghamim.
\v 11 \x - \xo 6:11 \xt Aposel 13:51\x*Ia kamagh…®n damu mang…® nguibatam…®n mang…®ght…®, me ian aghuagh ia inigh uan d…®penibar mang…®ghan kogh, egh uaghan ia m…®geir akaba baraghan koght…®ma, ia kamagh…®n damu. Ia nguibar kam ategh mang…®s…® uan dagarir m…®neziba apezegh, nguibar kam ategh mang…®. Ia kamagh…®n damight…®, me ganigh fogham, me arazir aghuim ia gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 6:11 \ft Judabar arazim kara, n…® me baraghan koght…®ma, me n…®n sagh, uan dagarir asuaba m…®neziba ap…®zigh…®va n…® ategh igharagh mangam. Ez…® en arazim kamak…®n, k…® n…® m…®k…®mt…® n…® na baraghan koght…®, k…® apem ap…®righ uan tuavim gighuvagh, egh suam, k…® n…®n sagham.\f*
\p 
\v 12 A kamagh…®n me m…®kemegha me amadaz…® me nguibabar ghua God…®n akam akura ghaze, Ia uan navibagh iragh.
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt Jems 5:14\x*Me kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava, egha uaghan gumazir av…®ribar duar kuraba batogha ar…®mariar gumazir av…®riba borem…®n men dapanibagh inga me gamima, me ua dera.
\s1 Herot Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim…®n, f…®rim atu
\r (Matyu 14:1-12; Luk 3:19-20; 9:7-9)
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14-15 \xt Matyu 16:14; Mak 8:28; Luk 9:19\x*Iesus bizir av…®ribagh amiz…® an ziam otogha ekevez…®, gumazir av…®riba a g…®fo. Ez…® danganir kam…®n Atrivim Herot, a baraki. Men marazi kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúJon Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim aremegha ua d…®kafi. Kamagh…®n a mirakelbar amuamin gavgavim iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® men marazi kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúA Elaija.‚Äù
\p Ez…® marazi kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam, a mati fom…®ra ikezir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar m…®n ami.‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Me akar kabav geima, Herot da baregha a fo, a fom…®ra Jon…®n f…®rim atu. Kamagh…®n amiz…® a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fom…®ra m…®kemez…®, me Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim Jon…®n f…®rim atu, ez…® a ua d…®kafi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 17-20 \x - \xo 6:17-20 \xt Ofa Gami 18:16; 20:21; Matyu 14:4; Luk 3:19-20\x*Herot kamagh…®n amigha a fo, a fom…®ra uan dozim Filip…®n amuim Herodias ini. Ez…® Jon zurara kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúHerot, n…® arazir kuram gamuava uan dozim da an amuim ini.‚Äù Jon kamagh…®n m…®geima, Herodias a bagha guizbang…®ra navim isia, egha Jon…®n m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa a bagha puv…®ra Herot m…®gei. Ez…® Herot Herodias ifongez…® mogh…®n damuan aghuagha, uan gumazir mabav kemez…® me Jon…®n suiragha a inigha kalabus gat…®. Herot fo, Jon God…®n damazim…®n zuegha derazir gumazimra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Herot an atiatia, a inigha deragha an gari. Herot uaghan Jon m…®geir akaba baragha n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amua, ana akaba baraghasa ifonge.
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Herodias dat…®r…®gh…®n Jon…®n m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuavim bato. Herot…®n amebam a batezir dughiam otoz…®, a dughiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha isar ekiam gami. Ez…® Herodias Jon m…®soghamin dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n oto. Herot isar kam gamuava, uan ingangaribar gari gumazir ekiaba, ko uan m…®dorozir gumazibar gari gumazir ekiaba, ko Galilin itir gumazir ekiaba, a men diaz…®ma me a ko damasa ize.
\v 22 Me izegha isam apima Herodias…®n guivim izava me apir danganim…®n ghugha men guam…®n ighiam gizi. A ighiam gizima, Herot ko ikia apir gumaziba an ighiam…®n ganigha guizbang…®ra bar a gifongegha a bagha bar akonge.
\p Me bar akuegha, Herot kamagh…®n guivir igiam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bizir manam gifongegh nan azaragh. Eght…® k…® bizir kam n…® danigham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 \x - \xo 6:23 \xt Esta 5:3; 5:6; 7:2\x*A kamagh…®n a m…®kemegha, akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® bizitam gifongegh, na m…®k…®m. N…® k…® garir bizibagh ifongegh…®va, na m…®k…®m. K…® tong…®ra da bigh…®va, taba n…® danigham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Guivir igiar kam akar kam baregha, azenan izegha ghua kamagh…®n uan amebam m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmebam, k…® bizir tizim bagh an azaragham?‚Äù
\p Ez…® an amebam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúJon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim…®n dapanim.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® guivir kam akar kam baregha, zuam…®ra uamategha aven ghugha kamagh…®n Herot m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim…®n, dapanim itaritam dat…®gh na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 6:26 \xt Matyu 14:9\x*Ez…® Herot a baregha, an navim bar oseme. A faragha akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim m…®geima a ko apir gumaziba a baraki. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an an azangs…®zim pueghan kogham.
\v 27 Egha Herot a baraghav…®ra, akar gavgavim uan m…®dorozir gumazim m…®kemegha anemadaz…® a ghua kalabus…®n aven iraghugha Jon…®n f…®rim atu.
\v 28 A Jon…®n f…®rim atugha an dapanim inigha itarir mam gat…®gha a inigha izava guivir kam gan…®ngiz…® anenigha ghua uan amebam gan…®ngi.
\v 29 Ez…® Jon…®n suren gumaziba an ovevem baregha izava an kuam inigha ghua a mozim gat…®.
\s1 Iesus dagheba // 5,000…®n gumazibagh an…®di
\r (Matyu 14:13-21; Luk 9:10-17; Jon 6:1-13)
\p 
\v 30 \x - \xo 6:30 \xt Luk 10:9-10; 10:17\x*Ez…® Iesus…®n aposelba ua izegha an borogh…®n uari akufa. Egha me aruava amizir biziba ko akar me gumazibar sure gamizibar gun Iesus geghari.
\v 31 \x - \xo 6:31 \xt Mak 3:20\x*Dughiar kam gumazamizir av…®riba me bagha mang…®gh izegh gamima, me damamin dughiaba puvat…®. Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uarira na ko mang…®va gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mang…®va avughsam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a, egha me uarira bot inigha gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganir mam…®n zui.
\v 33 Me zuima, gumazamizir av…®riba men ganigha me g…®fo. Ez…® nguibabar itir gumazamiziba bar men faraghav…®ra ivegha ghua me zuir danganim…®n otifi.
\v 34 \x - \xo 6:34 \xt D…®boboniba 27:17; 1 Atriviba 22:17; 2 Eghaghaniba 18:16; Esekiel 34:5; Matyu 9:36\x*Ez…® Iesus ghua d…®par dadarim…®n otogha garima, gumazamizir bar av…®riba iti. A men gari, me mati sipsipbar m…®n amua, ghuaviba puvat…®gha asaghasazibar m…®n puram arui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a bar men apangkufi. Egha a bizir av…®ribar men sure gami.\f + \fr 6:34 \ft N…® sipsip…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\p 
\v 35 \x - \xo 6:35 \xt Matyu 14:15; Mak 8:1-9; Luk 9:12\x*A m…®g…®av…®ra itima, am…®nim p…®riz…® an suren gumaziba a bagha iza kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim, ez…® am…®nim p…®ri.
\v 36 N…® gumazamiziba amadaght…®, me mang…® danganir kam…®n itir nguibaba ko rogh…®ra itir nguibar dozibar mang…®va me dam…®s…® uari bagh daghebagh ives.‚Äù
\p 
\v 37 \x - \xo 6:37 \xt D…®boboniba 11:13; 11:22; 2 Atriviba 4:43; Matyu 14:16; Luk 9:13; Jon 6:7\x*Ez…® a me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uari daghetaba me dan…®ng.‚Äù
\p Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDag…®ar e me bagh bretbagh ivezamim, a 200 kinan tu. E da inigh, mang…®, me bagh bretbagh ivezegh me dan…®ngasa, n…® ifonge?‚Äù\f + \fr 6:37 \ft Grigh…®n akam kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazim bretba kamagh…®n ives…®va, an 8plan iak…®nibar ingarigham.\f*
\p 
\v 38 Ez…® Iesus men azara, ‚ÄúIa manmagh…®ra bretba iti? Ia mang…® ganigh.‚Äù
\p A m…®kemez…®, me ghua ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bar bret…®n rubuzir 5pla ko osirir pumuningra iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 39 Ez…® Iesus me m…®kemez…® me gumazamizibav gei, me uari uari tuiragha grazim gapia.
\v 40 Ez…® me uari tuiragha okoruabar apiaghiri. Ez…® okoruar maba 50plan gumazamiziba iti, ez…® okoruar maba 100plan gumazamiziba iti.
\v 41 Me apiaghav itima, Iesus bret…®n 5pla inigha, osirir pumuning inigha, p…®n overiam…®n gara God m…®nabagha bretba ab…®aghar…®ki. Egha uan suren gumazibav geima, me da isa, gumazamizibagh an…®di. A uaghan osirimning sara ab…®aghar…®ghiz…®, me da isa, me gan…®di.
\v 42 Ez…® gumazamizir kaba bar amegha, naviba bar izefe.
\v 43 Men naviba bar izevez…®ma Iesus…®n suren gumaziba, dagher nar me ataghiziba inigha, ak…®rar 12pla gaghuiz…®ma, da bar iz…®fa.
\v 44 Dagheba amezir gumazibara, men d…®bobonim 5,000…®n tu.
\s1 Iesus d…®pam gis…®n tugha zui
\r (Matyu 14:22-36; Jon 6:16-21)
\p 
\v 45 Gumazamiziba amegha g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus kamagh…®n uan suren gumazibar ariragha ghaze, Ia bot…®n b…®nigh…®va faragh Betsaidan nguibam…®n vong…®n mang…®. K…® uab…®ra ik…® gumazamiziba amadaght…® me ua uan nguibabar mangam.
\v 46 \x - \xo 6:46 \xt Mak 1:35; Luk 5:16; 6:12; 9:28\x*A me amadaz…® me ghuez…®, a God ko m…®k…®masa m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuavanabo.
\p 
\v 47 Dughiar kam am…®nim p…®rima, men bot d…®pam…®n tong…®n itima, Iesus uab…®ra dadarim…®n iti.
\v 48 A ikiava uan suren gumazibar garima, am…®nir gavgavim izava men bot givai. Me pul gamua ingangarir dafam gamuava am…®nim ko uari adosi. Egha am…®nim tiasava amima, Iesus d…®pam gis…®n arua me bagha izi. A mang…® me gitagh mangasa.
\v 49-50 \x - \xo 6:49-50 \xt Matyu 14:26; Luk 24:37; Jon 6:19\x*Ez…® me an gari, a d…®pam gis…®n arua izima, me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúKar ti duatam.‚Äù
\p Me n…®ghn…®zir kam gamua, bar an ganigha puv atiatiava arai. Me araima, a zuam…®ra kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gavgafigh, kar k…®rara. Ia atiatingan mark…®!‚Äù
\v 51-52 \x - \xo 6:51-52 \xt Mak 4:39; Mak 8:17\x*A kamagh…®n me m…®g…®ava, me gat…®n bot…®n aven ghuz…®, am…®nim pura dutugha ghu. Ez…® Iesus 5,000plan gumaziba bretba me gan…®ngiz…® me damez…®, me bizir kabar ganigha, tong bar fozir puvat…®. Men n…®ghn…®ziba otefe. Egha me bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gh guizbang…®ra d…®gavir kuram gami.\f + \fr 6:51-52 \ft Dughiar kam…®n Iesus bret gumazamizibagh an…®gava, uan gavgavim men akakasi, me kamagh…®n ganigh suam, a bizir bar av…®rir igharagha garibar amuamin gavgavim iti. Ez…®ma an suren gumaziba bizir kabar garava a dagh fozir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n me Iesus…®n garima a d…®pam gis…®n aruava am…®nim gamiz…®ma an am…®raz…®ma me ganighava d…®gavir kuram gami.\f*
\s1 Iesus Genesaret…®n // ar…®mariar av…®riba ag…®fa
\r (Matyu 14:34-36)
\p 
\v 53 Egha Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko d…®pam…®n vong…®n ghugha, ghua Genesaret…®n nguibam…®n otivigha, bot ike.
\v 54 Me bot…®n ikegha dadarim…®n anadima, gumazamiziba Iesus…®n garav…®ra a g…®fo.
\v 55 Me a g…®fogha, egha gumazamiziba Iesus itir danganim baregha, ivegha danganir kam garua uan ar…®mariar gumazamiziba inigha me akuriabagh arigha Iesus bagha izi.
\v 56 \x - \xo 6:56 \xt Matyu 9:20; 14:36; Aposel 19:12\x*Iesus nguibar ekiaba ko nguibar doziba ko ruarir nguibabar zui. A zuir nguibar kaba me arazir kamram ami, me ar…®mariar gumazamiziba inigha iza nguibam…®n tong…®n da ar…®gha, egha a gakaghora ghaze, a men asught…®ma, ar…®mariaba itiba an korotiar av…®zibar suigham. Ez…® gumazamizir an korotiam…®n suiziba, men ar…®mariaba gefi.
\c 7
\s1 God…®n Araziba // Judan ovavibar arazibagh afira
\r (Matyu 15:1-9)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Farisin gumazir maba ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumazir maba, me Jerusalem…®n ikegha, izaghira, Iesus bagha izava anekufa.
\v 2 \x - \xo 7:2 \xt Luk 11:38\x*Me iza ikia garima, Iesus…®n suren gumazir maba men ovavibar arazibar g…®n ghua dafariba rua dagheba apir puvat…®. Me pura dagheba api.
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt Mak 7:5; 7:8; Jon 2:6; Galesia 1:14\x*Farisin kaba ko Judan gumazamiziba bar, me uan ovavibar arazibar suighav…®ra ikia, dafariba ruava api. Me pura daghebar aman kogham.
\v 4 \x - \xo 7:4 \xt Matyu 23:25\x*Me uaghan maket…®n inigha izir dagheba, me dar aman kogham. Me faragh da ruegh egh dar amam. Me uaghan uan ovavibar arazir av…®rir maba sara suighav…®ra iti. Me pura dagheba isamigh dar ameghan kogham. Me faragh uan m…®neba ko itariba ko apir dakoziba, ruegh…®va egh me dagheba isamam.
\p 
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Farisiba ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me Iesus…®n azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…® n…®n suren gumaziba en ovavibar arazibar g…®n mang…® dafariba ruan aghuagha, pura dagheba api?‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 \x - \xo 7:6-7 \xt Aisaia 29:13; Matyu 15:8-9\x*Ez…® Iesus me ikaragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uarira uarigh ifarir gumazibara. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia, a guizbang…®ra ia amir arazibar gun m…®g…®a kamagh…®n osiri:
\b
\q1 ‚Äú ‚ÄòGumazamizir kaba, me uan akatoribar nan ziam fe,
\q2 egha men naviba ko n…®ghn…®ziba bar saghon iti.
\q1 
\v 7 Me gumazibar akabar uari sure gamua
\q2 uari gifara egha ghaze, kar God…®n akam.
\q3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me nan ziam guizbang…®ra a fer puvat…®.‚Äô
\b
\m 
\v 8 ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n amua, God…®n akaba, ategha, uan ovavibar arazibar suiragha gavgafi.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 A m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa ghaze, ia arazir aghuim gamua God…®n akaba ategha uan arazibar g…®n zui. Ian arazir kaba bar ikufi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 7:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 20:12; 21:17; Ofa Gami 20:9; God…®n Araziba 5:16; Matyu 15:4\x*Moses fom…®ra kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄòIa uan afeziaba ko amebabar akaba baragh men apengan ik…®, egh gumazitam akar kuratam uan afeziam ko amebam m…®kemeght…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.‚Äô
\v 11 Ez…® ia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGumazitam uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akurvaghasa dag…®aba at…®gha, egha ua g…®n aning…®n akuraghan aghuagha, kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuan akuraghasa at…®zir dag…®aba, gua mark…®. K…® da is…® God dan…®ngam.‚Äù ‚Äô
\v 12 Ia kamagh…®n m…®geima, gumazir kam bizitam uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akurvazir puvat…®.
\v 13 Ia kamagh…®n amua, uan ovaviba da inizir arazibar g…®n ghua, da gumazir igharazibagh an…®di. Ian arazir kabar, ia God…®n Araziba ategha, uan ovavibar araziba faragha da ar…®si. Egha God…®n akam gamima a mati pura bizim. Ia amir bizir av…®rir maba uaghan iti.‚Äù
\s1 God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir biziba, // Iesus dav gei
\r (Matyu 15:10-20)
\p 
\v 14 Egha Iesus ua uab…®n borogh…®n itir gumazamizibar diaz…®ma, me a bagha izima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa bar na baragh, nan akar kaba deraghv…®ra dagh fogh.
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 7:15-16 \xt Aposel 10:14-15\x*Bizitam azenan ikegh gumazim…®n navim…®n aven mag…®r…® an navir averiam damight…®, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. Puvat…®, gumazim…®n navim…®n aven ikegha azenan izezir biziba, an navir averiam damight…®, a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zegham.‚Äù\f + \fr 7:15-16 \ft Bizir apiba azenan ikegha ghuaghira gumazim…®n muriar averiam gamima a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zezir puvat…®. Ez…® bizir kurar navim…®n aven ikegha azenan iziba a gamima an navir averiam m…®ze.\f*
\p 
\v 17 Iesus akar kaba gumazamizir av…®ribav kemegha, me ategha ghua d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®ma, an suren gumaziba akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim bagha an azara.
\v 18-19 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúEee! Ia ongani? Ia uaghan akar kam derav…®ra a g…®fozir puvat…®? Ia bizir kam g…®fo? Daghetam guizbang…®ra gumazim…®n navir averiam…®n mag…®r…®gh ikeghan kogham. Bizir akatorim…®n aven zuiba ghua navim…®n zuima, muriam da batozima, gumazim dagh avi. Kamagh…®n gumazim apir bizitam azenan ikegh an akam ko muriam…®n mag…®r…®gh, an muriam damight…® a God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham.‚Äù (Iesus akar gavgavim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, dagheba bar God…®n damazim…®n bar zue. Ez…® e dar amam.)
\p 
\v 20 \x - \xo 7:20 \xt Matyu 15:18; Mak 7:23\x*A m…®g…®a ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazim…®n navim…®n aven ikegha azenan izezir biziba, an arazir kuraba, a gamima, an navim God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.
\v 21 Gumazim…®n navim…®n aven ikegha azenan izezir arazibar kara, n…®ghn…®zir kuraba, gumazamiziba tintinibar uari koma akui, biziba okei, gumazamizibav sozi da ariaghiri,
\v 22 poroghamiba uari bakei, m…®gh…®ghav…®ra bizibagh ifonge, gumazamizir igharazibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa n…®ghn…®si, ifavariba, aghums…®ziba puvat…®zir arazir kuraba, bizim bagha navim ikufi, gumazir igharazim…®n ziam gas…®ghas…®si, uab…®ra uab…® fe, arazir onganiba,
\v 23 arazir kurar kaba bar navim…®n aven ikegha azenan iza, gumazim gamima a God…®n damazim…®n m…®ze.‚Äù
\s1 Fonisian amizim n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n iti
\r (Matyu 15:21-28)
\p 
\v 24 Egha Iesus Genesaret ategha Tair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n danganim…®n ghu. A gumazamiziba a g…®foghan an aghuagha, mogomebar ghua d…®penir mam…®n aven ghugha egha modozir puvat…®. Me bar fo, a d…®penim…®n aven iti.
\v 25 A d…®penir kam…®n itima, guivir duar kuram apazazim…®n amebam, a Iesus izezir darorim baregha, zuam…®ra a bagha izava an dagarimning…®n borogh…®n uan tevimning ap…®ri.
\v 26 Amizir kam, an amebam Fonisian Distrigh…®n a bate. A Sirian danganir ekiam…®n aven itir distrik. Egha a Grigh…®n akam m…®gei. A duar kurar an guivim gapazazim batoghasa Iesus m…®g…®ava a gakaghori.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE faragh boribar dagheba me dan…®ngt…®, me damam. Arazir kuram, k…® boribar dagheba inigh afiabav k…®nam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® amizim kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir Ekiam, K…® fo, afiar doziba uaghan boribar dakozim…®n apengan irezir dagher muzuemziariba api.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am dera. Kamagh…®n n…® uamategh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®. Duar kurar kam n…®n guivim ategha azenan ize.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® a uamategha uan d…®penim…®n ghua garima, an guivim uan dakozim gir…®ghav iti. Ez…® an an ganigha fo, duar kurar kam anetegha azenan ghu.
\s1 Iesus gumazir kuarir onganir mam…®n akuraz…®ma a dera
\p 
\v 31 \x - \xo 7:31 \xt Matyu 15:29-31\x*Egha Iesus d…®kavigha Tair…®n danganim ategha, ghua Saidon…®n danganim…®n otogha ghua, Dekapolis…®n Distrigh…®n otogha ghua, Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n dadarim giraghu.
\v 32 \x - \xo 7:32 \xt Matyu 9:32; Luk 11:14\x*A ghuz…®ma, gumazir maba gumazir kuarir onganir mam inigha Iesus bagha izi. Gumazir kam uaghan m…®zem osemegha derav…®ra m…®geir puvat…®. Me izegha dafarim a dar…®ghasa Iesus gakaghori.
\p 
\v 33 \x - \xo 7:33 \xt Mak 5:23; 8:23; Luk 4:40; 13:13; Jon 9:6\x*Ez…® Iesus gumazir kam inigha gumazir av…®riba ategha aning uaningra m…®riam…®n ghugha, egha a uan akakazir dafarimning gumazim…®n kuarimning gat…®gha aning asigha, egha iparigha, an m…®zem…®n suira.
\v 34 \x - \xo 7:34 \xt Jon 11:33; 11:38; 17:1\x*Egha Iesus p…®n overiam…®n garava, gumazir kam bagha navim bigha ara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEfata!‚Äù (Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúKuighir…®gh!‚Äù)
