\c 8
\s1 Iesus 4,000…®n gumaziba // dagheba me gan…®di
\r (Matyu 15:32-39)
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, gumazamizir av…®rir igharaziba iza uari akufa. Me damamin dagheba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Iesus uan suren gumazibar diaz…® me a bagha izima a kamagh…®n me m…®gei,
\v 2 \x - \xo 8:2 \xt Matyu 15:32-39; Mak 6:34-44\x*‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba, me na ko aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ikia, egha dagheba puvat…®gha m…®tiriam men azi, kamagh…®n k…® men apangkufi.
\v 3 Men marazi saghon ikegha ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® me amadaght…®, me m…®tiriaba sara, uan nguibabar mang…®va damaziba men isirt…®ma me iram.‚Äù
