\v 4 Ez…® an suren gumaziba kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúKar gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim. Ez…® e managh bretba inigh gumazamizir kabar an…®ngam?‚Äù
