\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt Luk 12:1\x*Ez…® Iesus akar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa deragh uari bagh gan! Ia derav…®ra Farisibar yis ko Herot…®n yis bagh derav…®ra gan.‚Äù\f + \fr 8:15 \ft N…® yis…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghs…®, ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
