\v 17 \x - \xo 8:17 \xt Mak 6:52\x*Me uarira uariv geima, Iesus men m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh fogha kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha ghaze, e bret tam inigha izezir puvat…®? Eee, ia k…® amir bizibar garava, fozir puvat…®. Ia t…®ghar deraghv…®ra dagh fofogham? Ian n…®ghn…®ziba bar otefe.
\v 18 \x - \xo 8:18 \xt Jeremaia 5:21; Esekiel 12:2; Mak 4:12; Aposel 28:26\x*Ia damaziba ikia, garir puvat…®? Ia kuariba ikia, orazir puvat…®? Ia bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®?
