\ms1 Iesus uan suren gumazibar // sure gami
\mr (Sapta 8:22--10:52)
\s1 Iesus Betsaidan gumazir damazir kurar mam…®n akuraz…®, an damazimning ua dera
\p 
\v 22 Egha me Betsaidan ghuez…®ma, gumazir maba gumazir damazir kurar mam inigha, Iesus bagha izi. Me izegha dafarim a dar…®ghasa Iesus gakaghori.
\v 23 Ez…® Iesus gumazir damazir kuram…®n agharim…®n suiragha, a inigha nguibam ategha azenan ghu. Aning azenan ghugha, Iesus gumazim…®n damazimning giparigha uan dafarimning a gis…®n at…®gha kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® bizitam…®n gari?‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® gumazir kam kogha gara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAre, k…® garima, gumazamiziba temebar m…®n garav arui.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® Iesus ua uan dafarimning an damazimning…®n suiraz…®, gumazim…®n damazimning kuiaghir…®z…®ma, a ua deragha bizibar gari.
