\v 28 \x - \xo 8:28 \xt Mak 6:14-15; Luk 9:7-8\x*Ez…® me a ikaragha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMarazi ghaze, n…® Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim. Ez…® marazi ghaze, n…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elaija. Ez…® marazi ghaze, n…® fom…®ra ikezir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam.‚Äù
