\v 29 \x - \xo 8:29 \xt Matyu 16:16; Mak 9:9; Jon 6:68-69; 11:27\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúEz…® ia? Ia tina na gar…®si?‚Äù
