\v 31 \x - \xo 8:31 \xt Matyu 17:22\x*Egha Iesus men sure gamua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizibar Otarim bar m…®zazir ekiaba koma os…®mt…®ziba iniam. Eght…® Judabar gumazir aruaba, koma ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, koma Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, me an aghuagh…®va a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Egh dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…® a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù
