\v 34 \x - \xo 8:34-35 \xt Matyu 10:38-39; Luk 14:27\x*Egha Iesus gumazamiziba ko uan suren gumazibar diaz…®, me a bagha izima, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazitam nan g…®n iz…®s…®, a ifongezir biziba g…®n amadagh uan ter ighuvim gisaghpugh nan g…®n iz…®.
\v 35 \x - \xo 8:35 \xt Luk 17:33; Jon 12:25\x*Gumazamizir manam uan ik…®r…®m…®rim suiraghs…® n…®ghn…®ght…®, an ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®vagham. Eght…® gumazamizir manam, Akar Aghuim ko na bagh uan ik…®r…®m…®rim ategh…®va, uan ik…®r…®m…®rim iniam.
\v 36 Gumazitam o amizitam nguazim…®n itir biziba bar da inigh a g…®n oveght…®, bizir kaba manmagh…®n an akuragham? Bar puvat…®.
\v 37 A ivezir manam uan duam bagh aneren…®ngam? Bar puvat…®.
\v 38 \x - \xo 8:38 \xt Matyu 10:33; Luk 9:26; Rom 1:16; 2 Timoti 1:8\x*Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n itir gumazamiziba me God ak…®rim ragha a gasaragha arazir kurabagh ami. Men tina nan ziam ko nan Akar Aghuim…®n gun m…®k…®man aghums…®ght…®, g…®n Gumazamizibar Otarim uan afeziam…®n borogh…®n ikegh…®va God…®n damazim…®n zuezir enselba koma God…®n angazangarim sara izighir…®, uaghan men aghums…®gham.‚Äù
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt Matyu 16:28; 24:30; 24:34; Mak 13:30; Luk 9:27\x*Iesus ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ia kagh tuivighav itir darasi, ian tarazi oveghan kogham. Ia ik…®v…®ra ik…® gant…®ma, God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam gavgavim sara izighiram.‚Äù
\s1 Iesus…®n m…®karzim igharagha oto
