\v 2 \x - \xo 9:2-7 \xt 2 Pita 1:17-18\x*Ez…® dughiar 6pla g…®vaz…®ma, Iesus Pita ko Jems ko Jon inigha m…®ghs…®ar ekiar mam…®n ghuavanabogha, me uarira kagh iti. A kagh an m…®karzim men damazim…®n igharaghav oto.
\v 3 \x - \xo 9:3 \xt Daniel 7:9\x*An korotiabar angazangarir gavgavir kam guizbang…®ra ghurghuri. Ghurghurir kam nguazim…®n gumazitam ruezir bizir ghurghuritam an m…®n garir puvat…®.
\v 4 Me garima Elaija ko Moses otogha Iesus ko me uariv gei.\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Moses ko Elaija bar fom…®ram ovengez…®ma, Iesus bogh…®mra nguazir kam…®n ize.\f*
