\v 5-6 Me uariv g…®av…®ra itima, Pita, Jems ko Jon me bar atiatigha, Pita m…®k…®mamin m…®g…®r…®g…®abagh asagha pura kamagh…®n Iesus m…®gei, ‚ÄúTisa, bar deragha e kagh iti! E purirpenir pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n ingaram. N…® bagh tam, Moses bagh tam, egh Elaija bagh tam.‚Äù
