\v 9 \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Matyu 12:16; Mak 8:30\x*Egha me uamategha m…®ghs…®am…®n izaghira Iesus bizir otozir me ganizim…®n gun gumazitam m…®k…®man bar men anogoroke. Kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® Gumazamizibar Otarim aremegh ua d…®kavigham.
\v 10 Me ganizir bizir kam merara iti, ez…® me aremegh ua d…®kavighamin m…®g…®r…®g…®ar m…®ngarim bagha uarira uariv gei.
\p 
\v 11 \x - \xo 9:11 \xt Malakai 4:5; Matyu 11:14\x*Egha me an azara, ‚ÄúManmaghsua Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba ghaze, Elaija faragh izeght…®, God Ua e Iniasa M…®sevezir Gumazim g…®n izam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 9:12 \xt Aisaia 53:3; Daniel 9:26; Malakai 4:5; Luk 23:11; Filipai 2:7\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men azangs…®zim ikara, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra Elaija faragh izegh…®va bizibar k…®ram. Ez…® tizim bagha fom…®ra God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n osizirim kamagh…®n iti, ‚ÄòGumazamizibar Otarim os…®mt…®zir av…®ribar aven mang…®t…® me ak…®rim a gasaragham?‚Äô
\v 13 \x - \xo 9:13 \xt Matyu 11:14; 17:12; Luk 1:17\x*Ez…® k…® ia m…®gei, Elaija izegha g…®fa. Ez…® gumazamiziba ak…®nafarim…®n osizirir an gun m…®kemezim…®n m…®rara, me uan arazir me ifongezibar a gami.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Dughiar kam…®n Iesus Elaija izamin bizim m…®gei, egha guizbang…®ra Jon, Gumazamiziba Ruer Gumazim m…®gei. N…® foghs…®, Matyu 17:12…®n gan. Jon izava Iesus izasava a bagha tuavibar ak…®ra faragha ize.\f*
\s1 Iesus otarir duar kuram apazazim gamiz…®ma // a ua dera
