\v 25 Egha Iesus garima gumazamiziba ivemara men borogh…®n zuima a duar kuram batogha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® duar kurar gumazamizibagh ami me orazi puvat…®zim ko m…®geir puvat…®zim, k…® n…® m…®gei, azenan iz…® egh uam aven mangan mark…®!‚Äù
