\v 28 Egha Iesus d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®ma an suren gumaziba mogomem…®n kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh amiz…®, e duar kurar kam batoghava avenge?‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúDuar kurar kamagh…®n amiba God ko m…®geir arazim…®n gavgavim…®n azenan izi.‚Äù
\s1 Namba 2…®n dughiam Iesus ghaze, // an aremegh ua d…®kavigham
\r (Matyu 17:22-23; Luk 9:43-45)
\p 
\v 30-31 \x - \xo 9:30-31 \xt Mak 8:31; 10:32-34; Jon 7:1\x*Egha me danganir kam ategha Galilin Distrigh…®n otogha zui. Me ghuava Iesus uan suren gumazibar sure gami. Bizir kam…®n Iesus me iti nagh…®n gumazitam foghan an aghua. Me ghua, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe Gumazamizibar Otarim is…®va gumazibar dafarim dar…®gham. Eght…® me a m…®sueght…® an ovegham. Eght…® dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…® a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù
