\v 50 \x - \xo 9:50 \xt Matyu 5:13; Luk 14:34-35; Rom 12:18; Efesus 4:29; Kolosi 4:6; Hibru 12:14\x*Amangs…®zim a dera, egh a uan is…®ngt…®zim ateght…®, ia manmagh…®n a damight…® a ua s…®ngigham? Ia amangs…®zim inigh uari dar…®gh, egh uari ko navir am…®rizim…®n ik…®.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:49-50 \ft Ves 49 ko 50…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®riba aning…®n aven iti. Ez…®ma Grigh…®n akam deragha dar akar m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam fofozir gumaziba uaghan n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ram an itir puvat…®.\f*
