\v 7 \x - \xo 10:7 \xt 1 Korin 6:16; Efesus 5:31\x*\x - \xo 10:7-8 \xt Jenesis 2:24\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazim uan ameboghfeziaba ategh mang…®, a uan amuim ko aning uaning…®n porogham.
\v 8 Egh aning inivaf…®zir vam…®ram otogham. Aning ua gumazir pumuning puvat…®. Aning inivaf…®zir vam…®ra ikiam.
