\v 30 \x - \xo 10:30 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 25:9; Luk 18:30\x*egh gumazir kam dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazir kam…®n, God guizbang…®ra bizir a faragha itiba bar dagh afiragh a dan…®ngam. A d…®penir av…®riba, aveghbuaba, buaramiziba, amebaba, borir av…®riba, ko azenir av…®riba a dan…®ngam. Eght…® God…®n g…®n zuir gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®zir araziba a uaghan dar aven ikiam. Eght…® dughiar g…®n izamim zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim an a dan…®ngam.
