\v 32 \x - \xo 10:32 \xt Mak 8:31; 9:31\x*Egha me Jerusalem…®n ghuavanaga Iesus faraz…®ma, an suren gumaziba an g…®n ghua n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribagh amima, me ko zuir gumazamiziba atiati. Ez…® Iesus ua uan 12plan suren gumaziba inigha me m…®riam…®n ghuegha, a bizir a bativamibar gun me m…®gei.
