\v 34 Eght…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, me d…®bovir akabar a m…®k…®m, a gipar…®va, a fozorogh…®va, a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. An aremeght…®, dughiar pumuning ko m…®kezim g…®vaght…® a ua d…®kavigham.‚Äù
