\v 8 \x - \xo 13:8 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 15:6; Aisaia 19:2; Matyu 24:8\x*Kantrin mam…®n itir darazi d…®kavigh kantrin igharazim…®n itir darazi ko m…®sogham. Eght…® atrivir mam…®n adarazi d…®kavigh atrivir igharazim…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham. Danganir mabar dagheba bar puvarat…®ght…®ma, gumazamiziba m…®tiriamra ikiam. Eght…® m…®k…®mk…®ziba uaghan otivam. Os…®mt…®zir kaba faragh otivigham, eght…® nguazir kam g…®vamin dughiam t…®ghar…®. Os…®mt…®zir kaba mati, amizim otasa faraghav…®ra m…®zazim barazi mok…®n.
