\v 9 \x - \xo 13:9 \xt Akar Mogomem 2:10\x*\x - \xo 13:9-11 \xt Matyu 10:17-20; Luk 12:11-12\x*‚ÄúIa derav…®ra uarira uari bagh gan. Gumazitaba ia is…® nguibabar garir gumazibar an…®ngam. Egh me God ko m…®geir d…®penibar ia m…®sogham. Egh ia na bang…®n atriviba ko gavman…®n gumazir ekiabar damazibar tuiv, egh k…® amizir biziba ia dar gun me m…®k…®mam.
