\v 12 \x - \xo 13:12 \xt Matyu 10:21\x*‚ÄúAveghbuaba uarira uari is…® apanibar an…®ngt…® me me m…®soght…® me ar…®m…®ghiram. Eght…® afeziaba uan boriba uaghan kamagh…®ra me damuam. Boriba uan ameboghfeziabar akaba batogh…®va ovengamin arazibar me damut…®, me ar…®m…®ghiram.
\v 13 \x - \xo 13:13 \xt Matyu 10:22; Jon 15:21\x*Eght…® gumazamiziba bar nan ziam bang…®n ian aghuagham. Eght…® gumazamizir gavgavigh ik…® mang…® dughiar abuananam…®n otoghamiba, God men akurvagham.‚Äù
