\v 1 \x - \xo 14:1 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:1-27; Mak 11:18\x*Dughiar kam, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam, ko Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam, dughiar pumuningra ikiav…®ra itima, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba, ko Judan Arazibagh fozir gumaziba, arazir mogometam…®n Iesus…®n suiragh a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buri.\f + \fr 14:1 \ft N…® Israelia Gitazir Dughiam koma Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam…®n m…®ngariba g…®foghs…®, n…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n ak…®rang…®n itir Akar M…®ngaribar gan.\f*
\v 2 Egha me kamagh…®n uariv gei, ‚ÄúE isam…®n dughiam…®n an suighan kogham. E damut…® isam…®n itir gumazamiziba m…®dorozir ekiatam damigham.‚Äù
\s1 Amizir mam mughuriar aghuim zuir borem Iesus…®n dapanim ginge
