\v 7 \x - \xo 14:7 \xt God…®n Araziba 15:11\x*Onganarazibagh amiba zurara ia ko ikiam. Ia dughiar manam men akurvaghs…®, men akurvagh. K…® zurara ia ko ikian kogham.
