\v 12 \x - \xo 14:12 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:6; 12:14; 12:20; Matyu 26:17; Luk 22:7\x*Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiabar faragha zuir aruem…®n, Judan gumazamiziba arazir kam iti. Me faragh God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh sipsip…®n igiam inigh God danigh…®va an ofa damuam. Ez…® Iesus…®n suren gumaziba an azara, ‚ÄúN…® danganir manam…®n God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam…®n isam am…®s…® ifueght…®, e an mang…® biziba ak…®ram?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® a uan suren gumazir pumuning amaga kamagh…®n aning m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua nguibar ekiam…®n mang…®t…® gumazitam d…®par m…®nem ater iz…® gua batoght…®, gua an g…®n mang…®.
\v 14 D…®penir an aven zuim gua an mang…®va an ghuavim m…®k…®m suam, Tisa kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòNan danganir k…® uan suren gumaziba ko God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam…®n isam amamim a mana?‚Äô
\v 15 Eght…® a p…®n d…®penim…®n aven itir danganir ekiam ian akagham. Danganir kam biziba bar ikia e baghav…®ra m…®zuai. Eght…® ia danganir kam e uari bagh biziba bar adar k…®righ.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® an suren gumazimning me ategha nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghua garima biziba an m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n m…®rara ghuz…®, aning magh…®ra God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam bagha dagheba ko bizibar k…®ri.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® guarat…®gh…®n Iesus uan 12plan suren gumaziba ko otifi.
\v 18 \x - \xo 14:18 \xt Onger Akaba 41:9\x*Egha dagher dakozim…®n apiaghav ikia apava, Iesus kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, ian tav na is…® gumazir nan apanim gamibar agharim dar…®gham, a uaghan na ko ikiava api.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Me an akam baregha, naviba bar oseme. Egha me bar vaghvagha an azangs…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ti markiama?‚Äù
