\v 20 Ez…® a me ikaragha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir na ko bret isa itarir vam…®ram aghua, uam a isim, a gumazir na is…®va apanibar agharim dar…®ghamim, a ian 12plan mav…®ra.
\v 21 God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, gumazamizibar Otarim aremegham. Eght…® gumazir Gumazamizibar Otarim isava apanibar agharim gat…®zim, gumaka! A bar ikuvigham! Amebam a batezir puvat…®z…®, deraghai!‚Äù
\s1 Iesus bret ko wain // uan suren gumazibagh an…®ngi
